Anglo Is in Talks to Sell Unit to CSN, Votorantim, Estado Says

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-04-25T12:43:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-25/anglo-is-in-talks-to-sell-unit-to-csn-votorantim-estado-says.html
Anglo American Plc (AAL)  is in talks with
Cia. Siderurgica Nacional SA and Grupo Votorantim to sell its
fertilizer unit Copebras SA, newspaper  O Estado de S.Paulo 
reported, citing an unnamed person with knowledge of the deal.  Pranill Ramchander, a spokesman for Anglo in Johannesburg,
didn’t immediately return an e-mail and a phone message from
Bloomberg News seeking comment. Spokesmen for CSN and
Votorantim, who can’t be named because of company policy, didn’t
immediately return an e-mail and a telephone call.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in  Sao Paulo  at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 